00:22:02,798 --> 00:22:05,241
But it was important that we identified all this stuff.

487
00:22:05,241 --> 00:22:07,283
What are our immersion points?

488
00:22:07,283 --> 00:22:09,445
What are the goals for each section

489
00:22:09,445 --> 00:22:12,788
of this little gameplay movie that we're gonna make?

